STEP 1 — locate the entry. grep js/chips/ for "'{chip['id']}':" and read the whole
entry: description, simpleName, guideOverview, guidePinDescriptions, guideSections,
pinout[], gates[], and any header comment above it. Note what's thin or missing.

STEP 2 — get the real datasheet and VERIFY. Pull the actual datasheet PDF
(curl the URL to a temp file, then Read it with the `pages:` argument so you see
the real terminal diagram and function table — do NOT trust a WebFetch text
summary of a TI/Fairchild PDF, it hallucinates pinouts; issues.md C4). Check the
