STEP 3 — improve the docs (the main job). Rewrite/expand so the entry actually
teaches this specific part to someone who's never seen it:
  - description / simpleName: accurate and specific (fill simpleName if blank).
  - guideOverview: what it is, what it does, and why someone reaches for it — in
    a few tight sentences, not marketing. Call out anything genuinely notable
    about THIS part (e.g. an unusual pinout, active-low control, an asynchronous
