  // Source: <Manufacturer>, "<Exact datasheet title>", <doc number> (<date>).
  //   [Online]. Available: <URL>. Verified: <what you read — e.g. "terminal
  //   assignment + function table, page 1, read as 300-dpi PDF images">.
